Install the required dependencies: npm install express axios cors

Frontend (React)
Create a new React application using Create React App : npx create-react-app my-app
cd my-app
npm install chart.js react-chartjs-2 axios

Backend: Run the Node.js server.
bash : node server.js


Frontend: Start the React application. : npm start

#Notes
Replace 'your_weather_api_key' and 'your_crypto_api_key' with your actual API keys.
Make sure the APIs you use are properly configured and you adhere to their rate limits and terms of service.
Enhance error handling and UI/UX as needed for your production application.
